column1: #Text=" Wan says : " I 'm saving this animal .
#Text=" Huntsman says : " That animal 's our dinner .
#Text=" Huntsman says : " Well , looks like you 're all out of tricks , Wan .
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " I. Really .
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " I do n't know what he 's screaming about .
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " It has special healing properties .
#Text=So what did you do to that hunter ?
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " Spirits are able to take over a human body for a short time .
#Text=If I stayed in there any longer , I would 've killed him , which I did consider .
#Text=" Wan says : " Thanks for saving my neck .
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " I saw you save the cat deer from those hunters .
#Text=I 've never seen such an act of selflessness from a human before .
#Text=" Wan says : " Told you I was n't like the others .
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " Guess I underestimated you , human .
#Text=" Friendly spirit # 2 says : " Are you off to find another lion turtle city ?
#Text=But I think I 've had enough of humans for a while .
#Text=I 've decided to stay here and learn the ways of the spirits .
#Text=" Friendly spirit # 1 says : " What a great idea .
#Text=" Friendly spirit # 2 says : " That 'll be fun .
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " Oh , now , now , hold on .
#Text=" Wan says : " First time for everything , right ?
#Text=I 've never had a human as a pet before .
#Text=" Wan says : " The name is Wan .
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " Stinky is more accurate .
